Race.SummaryText:
Southwest Avoyelles Waterworks District Proposition
(Millage Renewal)

Summary:  10 year 6.70 mills property tax renewal for acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and/or operating the waterworks system of the Southwest Avoyelles Waterworks District, including all necessary facilities, machinery and equipment.
Race.FullText: Shall Southwest Avoyelles Waterworks District of the Parish of Avoyelles, State of Louisiana (the "District"), levy a six and seventy hundredths (6.70) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $16,950 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2011 and ending with the year 2020, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and/or operating the waterworks system of the District, including all necessary facilities, machinery and equipment?
